bandwagon . . . One more win and it's showdown Sunday, baby, in Anaheim Stadium 
with the 49ers . . . Two more wins in a row and the league orders an 
investigation . . . Crowd of 32,969 is all-time Anaheim low on big day, but 
folks probably misunderstood -- next year's opener will be in Baltimore. T.J. 
