<HEADLINE>
<P>
UCI WINS OPENER IN WOMEN'S SOCCER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The UC Irvine women's soccer team defeated Cal State Hayward, 6-0, in its 
season opener Sunday at Anteater Field. 
</P>
<P>
 Kim Franzen scored two goals and Tracie Manz had a goal and two assists for 
the Anteaters. Lori Muzzonigro had a goal and an assist and Christina Rivera 
and Amber Willingham each scored for UCI. 
</P>
<P>
 Hayward dropped to 0-2. 
</P>
</TEXT>
