<TEXT>
<P>
 * Frank E. O'Bryan has been appointed to the board of directors of First 
American Financial Corp. in Santa Ana and to the board of its principal 
subsidiary, First American Title Insurance Co. He succeeds Harold Kean, who 
retired last year. O'Bryan is chairman of the Spring Mountain Group, whose 
