<DOCNO> LA090594-0075 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 076298 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
September 5, 1994, Monday, Valley Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 5 
</P>
