<DOCNO> LA090594-0085 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 076308 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
September 5, 1994, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 7; Column 3; Foreign Desk 
</P>
