 The officer and the emergency rescue worker were treated at the hospital and 
released, officials said. 
</P>
<P>
 Johnson disturbed the bees when he bumped the wall of a building next door. 
The hive was between the frame and paneling. 
</P>
<P>
 Beekeepers estimated that 75,000 bees were in the hive. 
</P>
