<HEADLINE>
<P>
PREP FOOTBALL '94 / SEA VIEW LEAGUE; NEWPORT HARBOR 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 1993 RECORDS 
</P>
<P>
 OVERALL: 7-4 
</P>
<P>
 LEAGUE: 4-3 
